{"tid":689815,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【徵空置稅】陳茂波指空置稅研究接近尾聲","createTime":"2018-06-04T10:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T02:08:57.000Z","uid":174649,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7c316722f9557e5197e47287dd944049570f2bb8","tid":689815,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180604/large/1528095766_e77a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180604%2Flarge%2F1528095766_e77a.jpg&h=d1800387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n財政司司長陳茂波今早出席立法會財經事務委員會會議，公民黨立法會議員郭榮鏗關注政府空置稅時間表及會否考慮資產增值稅，陳茂波指針對一手樓空置稅的研究已接近尾聲，結果將很快公布，又重申無意推行資產增值稅。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，根據運房局數據，去年12月底及今年3月底已興建的未賣一手單位有9000伙，相較於每年18000伙的新供應目標，空置數字算大，亦影響政府努力造地的有效供應。<br />\n陳茂波亦提及，市場認為美國本月中會再次加息，相信今年內將進一步加息，港息於聯繫匯率下會上揚，對本地資產價格及經濟氣氛或有影響，市民置業前應衡量風險。"},{"pid":"5f193d97caddaf62cacb43deccdf1ac9d475df90","tid":689815,"uid":33868,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"研究完之後決定唔推"},{"pid":"0e190bf4a45a47924299646d4241a21b8ca6b96b","tid":689815,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"政府點會推低樓價丫<br />\n百害無一利"},{"pid":"65e428ac3c70661bcb766198fb067b82bdb496c0","tid":689815,"uid":22845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:08:01.000Z","msg":"空置10年以上樓宇，收100％重地稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2031f4cb1375815207352586e617e132e5229d1","tid":689815,"uid":5499,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:19:04.000Z","msg":"佢自己成手貨，點會推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b75921f3f9d0c95ef674c4cce1482897ce195cc","tid":689815,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:21:23.0